Get contacts for a lead, including enriched email and phone data. Returns both organization contacts and enrichable contacts with IDs, tagged with `source:'org'|'paid'`.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} to check enrichment status (`contact.enrichment.done`) on individual leads after a bulk enrichment was launched, or to find the `contact_id` needed by leadbay_enrich_contacts.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} as a substitute for leadbay_research_lead, which already includes enriched contacts in its return.
